                    <span>Any person looking to raise the level of their speaking needs to add this book to their library.  I personally own every book Lilly has published.  As a professional speaker myself and the author of, "10 Days to More Confident Public Speaking" (Warner Books), I appreciate the value of the information in Lilly's book and I recommmend this book to anyone.</span>
                  
